videos.headline: Georgia Tech  takes kickoff back 77-yards for TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech's Juanyeh  Thomas avoids Virginia defenders for a 77-yard kickoff return touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia's Perkins walks in TD
videos.description: Bryce Perkins extends Virginia's lead as he goes untouched for a 9-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech wins on FG in OT
videos.description: Wesley  Wells nails a 40-yard field goal, as the Georgia Tech takes down Virginia 30-27.
